{
  "stem": "24409.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And each time, we have more people, the Turkish-- Turk, he didn't realize these Turks, that this is not possible, with one ship-- that the ship will be snapped by the British, obviously.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, this is what [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Reuben Hecht was there too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And for me, I sent this woman, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Bernstein, down there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there was negotiations done, and I got to the contacts, which I have.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't have it prepared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I couldn't find it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had it yesterday, in my hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But in the meanwhile, I misplaced it again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "A contract for this ship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, people in the were freezing, and we didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And some money came from America, but there was still not enough money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I do not remember that somehow, we had money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I took Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Bernstein into the deal, because she was in charge of the money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we had some money, and we [? lifted ?] money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We wanted to keep money-- I wanted to have money to buy a ship, on my own, so I'm not [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] depending, anymore, on Greeks or Turks.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But this was the last ship I made.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It's a book out by-- very good book by-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] Ofer is her last name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Ofer, Dalia Ofer, of the Hebrew University.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "On the transport, she has a chapter-- Willy Perl's last ship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was the largest ship ever to be used in illegal transportation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The ship finally came, but how this was-- it was the ship there, and we didn't have the money to the man.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the Germans, the Austrians had come down, in the meanwhile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And the Germans threatened to send them back to Vienna, because they were justified.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
